org.netbeans.spi.project.ui

Class ProjectProblemsProvider.ProjectProblem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.netbeans.spi.project.ui.ProjectProblemsProvider.ProjectProblem
  • Enclosing interface:
    ProjectProblemsProvider

    public static final class ProjectProblemsProvider.ProjectProblem
extends Object
    Project metadata problem. Represents a problem in the project metadata which should be presented to the user and resolved.

      • resolve

        public Future<ProjectProblemsProvider.Result> resolve()
        Resolves the problem. Called by the Event Dispatch Thread. When the resolution needs to be done by a background thread, eg. downloading an archive from repository, the implementation directly returns a Future which is completed by the background thread.
        Returns:
        the Future holding the problem resolution status.
